title: 22 in. Steel Handle Snow Shovel
description: This classic flat outdoor snow shovel with wear strip makes helps lift snow to more evenly and easily clear out any walkway, driveway or patio. Plus, the 2-section design makes the tool easy to take apart and store during the off season. The shovel features a powder-coated steel handle with a D-shaped polypropylene grip as well as a polypropylene shovel with metal scraper blade.
